theorem Topology.interior_closure_idempotent_six {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    (A : Set X) :
    interior (closure
      (interior (closure
        (interior (closure
          (interior (closure
            (interior (closure
              (interior (closure A)))))))))) =
      interior (closure A) := by
  simp [Topology.interior_closure_idempotent]
